      <;> linarith
    · -- Case: b ≤ a, min a b = b
      simp [h₄, min_eq_right]
      <;> linarith
  linarith
```

This seems more straightforward:
- If `0 ∈ [[a, b]]`, then `0 ≥ min a b`.
- But `min a b > 0`, so `0 ≥ min a b > 0`, a contradiction.

